---
import BaseLayout from '../../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="Construction & Careers: Active Texas Workforce | TomorrowBeginsHere.com"
    description="Explore how data center developments create immediate construction trades employment and stable long-term operational careers in Texas."
>
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 border-b border-tech-blue/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-950/80 via-slate-900/95 to-tech-blue/80 z-0 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/texas-data-centers-network.png')] bg-cover bg-center z-0 opacity-15 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24 text-center">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-300 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-6 border border-amber-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm">Pillar 07 • Jobs & Careers</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                Construction is Jobs Now:<br><span class="text-amber-300">Keeping Our Trades Active</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
                During economic uncertainty, data center construction represents a reliable source of high-paying employment, keeping Texas building trades active and secure.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white relative">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
                
                <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-800 font-semibold mb-8">
                    Building one of these campuses puts hundreds of people to work: electricians, site crews, engineers, local trades and suppliers.
                </p>

                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    And right now that matters more than usual. While a lot of Texas construction has slowed down with the economy, data center projects are keeping our building industry busy.
                </p>

                <!-- Workforce Info Card -->
                <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 my-12 shadow-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-950 mb-3">Counter-Cyclical Economic Shield</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
                        While other sectors of the commercial building industry (like office towers and retail strips) have paused due to macroeconomic uncertainty, digital infrastructure spending continues to accelerate. For Texas building trades and local material suppliers, data centers represent a vital economic shield, ensuring steady backlogs of high-paying commercial projects.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-lg font-medium">
                    Then come the permanent roles once it is running: high-wage technical and maintenance jobs that stick around for the life of the facility.
                </p>

                <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12">

                <div class="text-center bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold">Finished the Pillars</p>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Return to Texas Data Centers Hub</h4>
                    <a href="/texas-data-centers" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-6 py-3 bg-tech-blue hover:bg-tech-blue/90 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors">
                        Return to Hub
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
